@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@refreshToken = paste-refresh-token-here
@redirectUri = http://localhost:3000/auth/callback

### 내 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Google OAuth 로그인 시작 URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google/authorize

### Google OAuth callback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "paste-google-oauth-code-here",
  "redirectUri": "{{redirectUri}}",
  "clientType": "WEB"
}

### Access token 재발급
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}",
  "clientType": "WEB"
}

### 로그아웃
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
